# changedTypesRemovedUserInfoKey

**Type Property**

With the notification named [doc://com.apple.uikit/documentation/UIKit/UIPasteboard/changedNotification], use this key to access the removed representation types. These types are stored as an array in the notification’s `userInfo` dictionary.

## Declaration

```swift
nonisolated class let changedTypesRemovedUserInfoKey: String
```

## Constants

- **changedTypesAddedUserInfoKey**: With the notification named [doc://com.apple.uikit/documentation/UIKit/UIPasteboard/changedNotification], use this key to access the added representation types. These types are stored as an array in the notification’s `userInfo` dictionary.
